column5: Well I was cruisin through some Corb Lund and this song came up. Then I remembered looking at your X-mas threads....enjoy  EDIT-This song could also apply to Worm Dangler
Can't say as I quite understand how its mine, but its a catchy tune and I like how he uses a chain saw

come on now!!!  i take care of my stuff ya i've given my truck quite a bit of character sleds been through the bush more then once haha broken fishing rods the list goes on but i make sure everything runs tip top just dont look to wonderful lol
This is why....I could see you ripping some pine up to laminate together for a cabinet using a Husq or a Stihl  Kidding   Oh thats one way of putting it
back in our drinking days.  ...you know what...I've never broken a fishing rod...my buddies dad leaned over the side of the boat and broke one on me once, but thats the only broken rod I ever had
you should have seen me down in the basement of the outhouse cutting out the floor this summer...Husqvarna 61  I have ripped a few maple boards with it
good tune but do you remember the rod out in garden Dara?
that was you that did that one  and how come you named yourself after a lake?   nice bass..that for dinner?
Reminds of an old girlfriend...hard on the equipment Great Video!
